<title>THE PRECIOUS NAME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu min chuh kivawp zing un,
 Sanggah, gimthei, liengvaite;
 Kipahna, muonna hun pie'n a,
 Na chieh nau cheng ah vawp un.

[V2]
 Min lulpen, hawihtak chuh!
 Lei lungtup leh van nawpna;
 Min lulpen, hawihtak chuh!
 Lei lungtup leh van nawpna.

[V3]
 2. Isu min chuh kivawp zing un,
 Phaw leh lum in sung zing un;
 Na vel a thepna a um leh,
 Pauchamna'n min thieng sam un.

[V4]
 3. Aw, Lal Isu min lultak chuh,
 Lungguk a kipahsak hi;
 Hehpihna ban a ei pawm tieng,
 I kam uh pak la'n a dim.

[V5]
 4. Lal Isu min chuh chawian in,
 A kengbul a bawkkhup in;
 Van ah Lalpen khuksak hitiu,
 I zinnau I zawh tieng leh.</lyrics>
</song>